  <scopecontent audience="internal" id="aspace_ef9d55cc82e28839238142785ce6a55a">
    <head>Content Description</head>
<p>The collection contains different models and types of e-book readers including the  Amazon kindle, Kindle fire, Nook color Barnes &amp; Noble (with leather cover), RCA eBook which inludes a folder of 2002 Gemstar reader newsletters.</p>  </scopecontent>
  <bioghist audience="internal" id="aspace_287a52ccb7f1760224a4f5585ed3938e">
    <head>Biographical / Historical</head>
<p>E-book readers are electronic devices that are designed primarily for the purpose of reading digital books and periodicals.</p>  </bioghist>
